WEBVTT

01:34.760 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:38.320 --> 01:42.000
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

01:44.840 --> 01:46.400
Here alone today?

01:48.120 --> 01:49.000
Want a bowl of noodles as usual?

01:50.040 --> 01:51.880
I want two bowls today.

01:51.960 --> 01:54.520
- Want the second one later?
- No, serve them together.

01:54.600 --> 01:55.640
Okay.

02:06.480 --> 02:10.320
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

02:13.280 --> 02:14.200
Here you go.

02:15.960 --> 02:17.680
- Thanks.
- Enjoy your meal.

02:41.160 --> 02:42.400
Hey.

02:42.480 --> 02:43.560
Are you nervous?

02:44.840 --> 02:46.480
No. And you?

02:47.080 --> 02:49.240
If you're not, then I can't be either.

02:50.080 --> 02:51.800
I'm at the noodle restaurant now.

02:54.560 --> 02:55.560
We made a promise.

02:56.560 --> 03:00.040
I will definitely go
to Nanwu University with you.

03:04.320 --> 03:05.240
BEIYU
NANWU

03:14.760 --> 03:15.960
3,144 DAYS

03:19.360 --> 03:21.200
You come home late without a word?

03:26.560 --> 03:28.640
Why did you get off work so early today?

03:30.880 --> 03:32.480
Senior Sang, sorry for the intrusion.

03:34.520 --> 03:35.680
What are you doing here?

03:35.760 --> 03:37.520
- I heard your lease is almost up.
- So?

03:37.600 --> 03:41.720
So, I'm about to take your place
as Yifan's next roommate.

03:45.480 --> 03:46.520
Next…

03:47.480 --> 03:48.840
room…

03:49.440 --> 03:50.600
mate?

03:50.680 --> 03:53.800
You might get too comfortable here
and not want to leave.

03:59.000 --> 04:01.120
I haven't even agreed to let you move in.

04:01.200 --> 04:02.880
Don't worry.

04:02.960 --> 04:04.760
I'll be a better roommate.

04:05.520 --> 04:09.320
I won't cause you any trouble
or be a burden.

04:09.840 --> 04:11.200
Would you mind if I look around?

04:13.200 --> 04:16.360
The kitchen is large and fully equipped.

04:16.880 --> 04:17.959
There's a dishwasher.

04:18.720 --> 04:21.640
It'll keep things clean. I don't
have to worry about washing dishes.

04:24.600 --> 04:25.440
And there's a range hood.

04:32.600 --> 04:35.720
Tell me. Senior Sang
is not a clean freak, is he?

04:36.880 --> 04:39.200
Living with someone like that
must be super stressful.

04:39.280 --> 04:41.800
Actually, you're the one stressing me out.

04:43.800 --> 04:45.680
Besides, he's pretty easygoing
most of the time.

04:47.760 --> 04:49.880
Then, let me check out my future room.

04:49.960 --> 04:51.320
- I refuse.
- I refuse.

05:01.080 --> 05:03.160
Mu, you're making this really awkward.

05:04.560 --> 05:06.520
Finding a roommate
was something from before.

05:07.080 --> 05:08.840
And today, you didn't even…

05:09.800 --> 05:12.680
check with Senior Sang first.
I think that's inappropriate.

05:13.960 --> 05:16.880
Yifan, everything
you just mentioned isn't a problem.

05:16.960 --> 05:20.600
A good roommate is harder to find
than a good apartment.

05:21.680 --> 05:24.040
If we become roommates,
I'll handle all the chores.

05:24.960 --> 05:27.800
We can go to work together,
come home together,

05:27.880 --> 05:30.120
cook meals together,
and look out for each other.

05:30.200 --> 05:31.440
Isn't that great?

05:32.520 --> 05:34.520
Mu, you should head home for today.

05:34.600 --> 05:35.520
If there's anything to discuss,

05:35.600 --> 05:37.440
let's wait until this place
is actually vacant.

05:37.520 --> 05:39.760
Also, I generally don't prefer
or feel comfortable

05:39.840 --> 05:40.680
living with male roommates.

05:42.160 --> 05:43.160
Then what about Senior Sang?

05:47.040 --> 05:49.160
He… He's an exception.

05:56.080 --> 05:57.480
Don't do this again.

06:05.000 --> 06:06.960
I never said I was moving out.

06:09.440 --> 06:11.360
I have no idea why he suddenly showed up.

06:12.240 --> 06:13.760
Maybe it's because…

06:14.280 --> 06:17.240
because Su Tian mentioned
that I was looking for a roommate,

06:17.320 --> 06:18.200
and he overheard.

06:18.280 --> 06:19.120
So…

06:19.200 --> 06:20.680
So, you really dislike
having me as your roommate?

06:20.760 --> 06:22.320
Of course not.

06:25.520 --> 06:26.640
It's just…

06:27.440 --> 06:29.280
It's just that your place
is almost finished renovating.

06:29.360 --> 06:33.160
I'm worried that if you suddenly move out,

06:33.240 --> 06:36.320
I'll be stuck paying the rent by myself.

06:37.200 --> 06:38.920
Didn't I already transfer
my share of the rent?

06:42.680 --> 06:43.760
So…

06:44.600 --> 06:46.240
How much longer will you stay?

06:47.000 --> 06:48.000
What about you?

06:49.520 --> 06:50.720
How long do you want me to stay?

06:56.080 --> 06:57.120
Maybe…

06:57.800 --> 07:00.360
until you get a girlfriend.
Then we can talk about it.

07:00.440 --> 07:02.080
I'm heading back to my room.

07:12.640 --> 07:14.560
One day, he'll move out.

07:17.400 --> 07:18.640
Why do I care so much?

07:35.600 --> 07:38.000
I really dislike this habit.

07:41.240 --> 07:44.240
And I fear getting used
to someone else's presence.

07:47.720 --> 07:49.800
It always leads to one of two outcomes.

07:50.600 --> 07:51.920
No matter what happens,

07:54.000 --> 07:54.880
I'll always be with you.

07:58.840 --> 08:00.040
You need to be ready for that.

08:00.880 --> 08:02.680
Director, is there
anything else we can do?

08:02.760 --> 08:04.200
Please, save him.

08:04.280 --> 08:06.560
You've done your best.
There's nothing to regret.

08:06.640 --> 08:08.800
I beg you. Please try again.

08:10.000 --> 08:11.120
I'm sorry for your loss.

08:11.920 --> 08:14.080
It could happen
just like it did with my father.

08:14.960 --> 08:16.240
Patient Wen Liangzhe…

08:16.320 --> 08:18.600
One day, out of nowhere…

08:18.680 --> 08:19.840
…44 years old…

08:20.360 --> 08:21.720
…he left me forever.

08:22.720 --> 08:24.160
…was declared clinically deceased

08:24.240 --> 08:28.760
at 14:04 p.m. on March 11
due to unsuccessful rescue efforts.

08:29.600 --> 08:30.880
Family, please accept our condolences.

08:31.400 --> 08:33.320
Jiang, hurry up.
We've been waiting for you.

08:34.159 --> 08:36.039
- Mind your step. Be careful.
- It's okay.

08:40.159 --> 08:41.679
Or it could happen
like it did with my mother.

08:42.840 --> 08:46.280
For her own sake, to have a better life,

08:48.680 --> 08:50.040
she chose to leave me behind.

08:52.000 --> 08:54.160
I hate how life is full of partings,

08:55.360 --> 08:56.680
always saying goodbye.

08:57.560 --> 08:59.440
Maybe it's better
not to get used to it at all.

09:00.200 --> 09:01.240
I can't get used to it.

09:01.760 --> 09:03.520
I shouldn't get used to it.

09:18.080 --> 09:19.680
Grandpa. What brings you here?

09:19.760 --> 09:22.720
I'm not here for you.
I'm here to see my granddaughter-in-law.

09:23.400 --> 09:24.480
Granddaughter-in-law?

09:25.080 --> 09:27.520
That's right. I'm here for Linlin. Linlin!

09:28.120 --> 09:29.240
- Zhong Siqiao.
- Hello?

09:29.320 --> 09:30.200
Zhong Siqiao. It's me, Su Haoan.

09:30.280 --> 09:31.760
I need your help, urgent.

09:32.440 --> 09:34.640
I'm busy. Ask someone else.

09:34.720 --> 09:37.320
Well, my grandpa is at my place.

09:37.400 --> 09:39.240
He says he's here to see Wang Linlin.

09:39.320 --> 09:42.080
Apparently, I got drunk one time
and told him

09:42.160 --> 09:43.960
that we're planning
to get married and have kids,

09:44.040 --> 09:46.440
and we're going to live together.

09:46.520 --> 09:48.240
Please come over now!

09:48.920 --> 09:51.400
- I'm busy.
- Busy with what?

09:53.160 --> 09:55.720
Come on. Please?
Just this once. I beg you.

09:55.800 --> 09:56.760
Zhong Siqiao!

10:10.600 --> 10:11.440
Grandpa,

10:12.160 --> 10:14.080
after getting supper,

10:14.160 --> 10:16.640
Linlin went to a friend's birthday party.
She won't be back tonight.

10:16.720 --> 10:18.880
I'll wait here until she gets home.

10:20.320 --> 10:22.000
By the way, let me ask you.

10:23.720 --> 10:24.560
Why haven't you gone

10:24.640 --> 10:26.360
to visit your parents'
and brother's graves?

10:30.240 --> 10:31.600
I'll find time to go.

10:31.680 --> 10:33.360
- Really?
- Really.

10:34.320 --> 10:36.600
I checked with the cemetery staff.

10:36.680 --> 10:39.080
No one else has visited
aside from your grandma and me

10:39.160 --> 10:40.560
in the past two years.

10:42.800 --> 10:43.680
Tell me.

10:44.200 --> 10:46.680
Do you really dislike them that much?

10:51.240 --> 10:53.080
I've been busy with work.

10:53.160 --> 10:54.480
My business is huge now, really.

10:54.560 --> 10:56.120
You'll see for yourself
next time you visit.

10:57.000 --> 10:58.800
How busy are you, really?

10:58.880 --> 11:00.040
Look at yourself.

11:00.120 --> 11:02.200
Drifting through your days, wasting time.

11:02.280 --> 11:04.440
Sooner or later, Linlin will leave you.

11:12.080 --> 11:15.200
- You're just getting back now!
- Grandpa, I'm home!

11:15.280 --> 11:16.840
Where did you go?

11:16.920 --> 11:18.040
We ran out of toilet paper at home,

11:18.120 --> 11:19.880
and there was a sale today,
so I went to buy some.

11:20.400 --> 11:23.160
Weren't you at your friend's
birthday party?

11:26.160 --> 11:28.440
Yeah! The supermarket
belongs to my friend's family.

11:28.520 --> 11:31.520
Since it was her birthday today,
they had a sale.

11:32.720 --> 11:36.400
Haoan, go buy a serving
of Nanwu's best soup dumplings

11:36.480 --> 11:39.000
at the same place I used
to take you when you were little.

11:39.080 --> 11:40.840
Grandpa, you already bought
late-night snacks.

11:40.920 --> 11:43.640
- Did you forget?
- They've been sitting for so long.

11:43.720 --> 11:45.000
Grandpa, I'm not hungry anyway.

11:45.080 --> 11:47.840
Yeah, she's not hungry. Me neither.

11:47.920 --> 11:49.120
What do you mean by that?

11:49.200 --> 11:51.560
You can buy handbags for Linlin

11:51.640 --> 11:54.160
but not soup dumplings for your grandpa?

11:56.520 --> 11:57.880
- Go!
- Go on!

11:58.560 --> 12:00.040
- Fine.
- Unbelievable.

12:08.200 --> 12:11.640
Linlin, I want to ask you a few things.

12:19.000 --> 12:23.200
Do you usually sleep on the left side
or the right side?

12:26.680 --> 12:28.560
- The right side!
- That's strange.

12:29.640 --> 12:32.400
Haoan has always slept on the right side.

12:32.480 --> 12:34.360
Yeah, I know.

12:34.440 --> 12:36.480
But I've also slept
on the right side since I was a kid.

12:36.560 --> 12:38.440
So, he lets me have it.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.080
Where are your clothes?

12:48.160 --> 12:50.640
Haoan said mine didn't look good.
He wants to buy me new ones.

12:50.720 --> 12:53.360
So, for now, I'm just wearing his.

12:53.440 --> 12:56.040
It's loose, comfy, and sweet!

12:59.360 --> 13:01.240
Are you two hiding something from me?

13:02.640 --> 13:04.200
This Haoan…

13:05.040 --> 13:06.240
He actually dared to lie to me!

13:07.440 --> 13:09.520
- Actually, I--
- You two aren't really living together,

13:09.600 --> 13:10.800
are you?

13:12.200 --> 13:14.320
- We--
- You're about to get married.

13:14.400 --> 13:16.160
What's wrong with living together?

13:16.920 --> 13:19.160
Or do you want to wait
until after the wedding

13:19.240 --> 13:21.760
to find out your husband snores so loudly

13:21.840 --> 13:24.200
that you can't sleep at night?

13:25.760 --> 13:28.520
That after work, he leaves
his clothes and socks everywhere

13:29.080 --> 13:30.560
and refuses to do housework?

13:32.440 --> 13:34.320
Your place is a mess!

13:38.120 --> 13:41.360
Grandpa, you're surprisingly open-minded.

13:41.440 --> 13:43.680
I was young once too.

13:44.800 --> 13:46.680
Love is blind.

13:47.600 --> 13:50.920
Haoan has always kept things to himself

13:51.440 --> 13:52.920
since he was little.

13:53.000 --> 13:55.720
You've been through a lot.
Be patient with him.

13:56.880 --> 13:58.240
I will, Grandpa.

14:03.280 --> 14:04.640
What happened here?

14:34.360 --> 14:36.760
When did it get so tidy?

14:51.640 --> 14:53.920
I made extra porridge. Help me finish it.

14:57.800 --> 14:59.200
I'll just have cereal.

15:03.360 --> 15:04.440
I'm heading out.

15:23.320 --> 15:25.240
I can't get used to all this.

15:26.360 --> 15:30.240
Going back to how things were
might be the best choice.

15:31.880 --> 15:34.040
If I get used to his presence…

15:35.960 --> 15:37.080
maybe…

15:38.640 --> 15:40.880
one day, it'll all disappear.

15:42.320 --> 15:44.200
NANWU TV STATION

15:59.680 --> 16:00.680
Morning, Yifan.

16:01.760 --> 16:02.880
Morning.

16:02.960 --> 16:05.560
This is the breakfast I specially prepared

16:06.640 --> 16:07.720
to share with you.

16:09.000 --> 16:10.920
I already ate. Have it on your own.

16:11.720 --> 16:12.720
Come on. Help me out.

16:12.800 --> 16:14.920
It's too much for me alone.
I can't finish it.

16:15.600 --> 16:17.800
- Good morning.
- Morning.

16:18.680 --> 16:19.720
Are you having breakfast?

16:21.680 --> 16:22.800
Try some.

16:25.760 --> 16:28.120
He made too much.
How about let Su Tian finish it for you?

16:28.800 --> 16:31.000
Great. I haven't eaten yet.

16:35.640 --> 16:37.360
Then I'll trouble you, Su Tian.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.800
You're pregnant.
You should eat more nutritious food.

16:38.880 --> 16:39.720
Thank you!

16:46.720 --> 16:48.080
Um… Yifan.

16:49.000 --> 16:50.440
I want to apologize.

16:50.960 --> 16:54.160
Yesterday…
Did I disturb you and Senior Sang?

16:55.760 --> 16:57.960
- A little.
- But I just don't get it.

16:58.560 --> 17:00.360
He's so cold and distant.

17:00.440 --> 17:03.440
Yifan, why do you force yourself
to live with him?

17:03.520 --> 17:05.800
You deserve a better roommate.

17:08.640 --> 17:10.119
I don't feel forced.

17:12.920 --> 17:13.960
Maybe I'm just used to it.

17:15.839 --> 17:17.160
Yifan,

17:17.240 --> 17:19.040
director Shen from
the finance department is looking for you.

17:19.920 --> 17:21.119
- Got it.
- Morning.

17:21.200 --> 17:23.240
- Chengyun, have you eaten?
- Morning.

17:23.319 --> 17:24.240
I bought two servings.

17:24.319 --> 17:25.960
- Want to share?
- Yifan.

17:26.040 --> 17:28.119
I hope you know
how to take care of yourself.

17:28.840 --> 17:32.520
You need to open your eyes
and see who truly cares about you.

17:32.600 --> 17:34.880
Don't always assume it's normal
for people to push you around.

17:34.960 --> 17:36.920
That's a bad habit. You should break it.

17:37.880 --> 17:40.560
Alright. Thanks for your concern.

17:46.440 --> 17:47.440
Also…

17:47.520 --> 17:50.840
I think I can tell
what's actually a bad habit.

18:02.640 --> 18:03.640
Mr. Shen.

18:03.720 --> 18:04.920
I sent the interview outline

18:05.000 --> 18:07.280
for Wanda Corporation
to your email last night.

18:07.360 --> 18:10.360
I've assigned Zhen Yu from your team
to handle the interview.

18:10.440 --> 18:12.280
Is there an issue with my outline?

18:13.560 --> 18:16.200
I heard about what happened at Yihe Daily.

18:17.440 --> 18:19.320
Even though that's your personal matter,

18:19.400 --> 18:23.240
Chairman Cao of Wanda
used it as a reason to reject you.

18:25.040 --> 18:26.080
You should head back for now.

18:32.320 --> 18:34.960
Step aside! You're Wen Yifan, right?

18:40.480 --> 18:43.200
People all have emotions and desires.

18:43.720 --> 18:45.720
But I won't criticize you here.

19:04.040 --> 19:07.120
Yifan, what's wrong? You look so upset.

19:17.800 --> 19:20.200
Yifan, are you okay?

19:41.600 --> 19:42.520
Hello?

19:44.320 --> 19:45.360
Got it.

19:47.400 --> 19:51.360
Yifan, the security guard downstairs
said someone is looking for you.

20:31.080 --> 20:33.000
This is the last time I'm coming here.

20:33.080 --> 20:34.040
I don't want to see…

20:36.480 --> 20:37.360
any of you ever again.

21:03.120 --> 21:04.600
What do you want from me?

21:06.760 --> 21:07.840
Jiang!

21:20.800 --> 21:24.040
I sent you a message before.
Did you see it?

21:25.560 --> 21:27.520
Your aunt has already gone back to Beiyu.

21:31.680 --> 21:34.480
- That day, I didn't think it through.
- How did you get in?

21:36.960 --> 21:37.800
I won't let her come to my house anymore--

21:37.880 --> 21:39.240
How did you get in?

21:42.280 --> 21:43.120
I'm your mother.

21:43.200 --> 21:45.720
Does that mean my feelings
don't matter to you?

21:55.000 --> 21:55.960
Jiang,

21:56.880 --> 21:59.400
I talked to your aunt recently.

21:59.480 --> 22:00.600
About what happened before,

22:00.680 --> 22:02.560
I wasn't there for you,
I didn't know the details,

22:02.640 --> 22:04.720
so, I didn't take your side.

22:05.240 --> 22:07.400
- I was wrong.
- Is that so?

22:07.480 --> 22:09.880
I always thought
they took good care of you.

22:10.400 --> 22:12.120
I felt reassured.

22:12.800 --> 22:15.400
At that time, I wanted to bring you back.

22:17.360 --> 22:18.880
But I was afraid
that moving around too much

22:18.960 --> 22:20.400
would affect your college entrance exams.

22:20.480 --> 22:22.440
How could I not be angry?
He was just drunk

22:22.520 --> 22:24.400
and went into the wrong room.

22:24.480 --> 22:26.000
She just randomly
put this accusation on him!

22:26.080 --> 22:28.960
I thought, after some time,
things would settle.

22:29.040 --> 22:31.880
Once you got into college in Nanwu,
I could take better care of you.

22:31.960 --> 22:33.280
I have to go now.

22:33.360 --> 22:35.280
Uncle Zheng drove me here.

22:35.360 --> 22:38.280
He's still waiting outside.
I can't make him wait too long.

22:38.360 --> 22:39.440
I'll call you later.

22:39.520 --> 22:41.160
Call her later?
Are you trying to run away?

22:41.240 --> 22:43.000
I never expected

22:44.200 --> 22:46.640
you'd end up going to Yihe University,
a place far away.

22:50.320 --> 22:52.200
If I returned to Nanwu,
would you have lived with me?

22:59.760 --> 23:00.840
Jiang,

23:02.320 --> 23:05.320
I'll make it up to you. Okay?

23:06.520 --> 23:09.760
Please… don't be mad at me anymore.

23:15.280 --> 23:17.160
Is there anything else you need to say?
I have to work now.

23:19.040 --> 23:22.760
I brought you some of your favorite food.

23:22.840 --> 23:25.240
- You're too thin. Take it.
- No need. Thanks.

23:25.320 --> 23:26.560
Jiang.

23:26.640 --> 23:27.680
Jiang!

23:28.560 --> 23:31.000
Take it, okay?
I already brought it. Just keep it.

24:02.680 --> 24:04.320
CLEAR CHAT HISTORY

24:04.400 --> 24:07.480
ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT TO DELETE
THE CHAT WITH ZHAO YUANDONG?

24:10.680 --> 24:12.400
DELETE

24:19.200 --> 24:20.480
Mr. Gan,

24:20.560 --> 24:22.680
we've worked together for so many years.

24:22.760 --> 24:24.720
- You know what kind of person I am.
- I can't hear you.

24:24.800 --> 24:27.320
I'm someone who means what I say.

24:27.400 --> 24:29.080
I don't do things carelessly.

24:29.840 --> 24:33.160
I came to see you today
mainly about Wen Yifan.

24:34.400 --> 24:37.600
Wen Yifan's affair
is spreading like wildfire

24:38.200 --> 24:40.160
- throughout the department.
- Yifan.

24:40.240 --> 24:41.520
- Everyone knows.
- Hello.

24:42.240 --> 24:43.760
- Hey…
- Do you think she's a mistress…

24:43.840 --> 24:45.360
Come with me to the restroom.

24:45.440 --> 24:46.720
- …or was she just kept by someone?
- Let me put my stuff down first.

24:46.800 --> 24:48.120
No need. Let's go.

24:48.200 --> 24:51.160
I never thought
Wen Yifan was that kind of person.

24:51.880 --> 24:54.920
- She's actually a mistress.
- She offended a client.

24:55.000 --> 24:56.480
Now the advertising department
is blaming us.

24:56.560 --> 24:58.360
How do you expect me to explain this?

24:58.920 --> 25:00.840
I'm so sick of these rumors.

25:04.360 --> 25:05.400
Excuse me.

25:09.320 --> 25:10.320
And you

25:10.400 --> 25:13.800
just sent her to my team
to build connections without a word.

25:15.760 --> 25:19.120
You know that the companies I interview

25:19.200 --> 25:21.720
for the finance column
are all potential clients.

25:21.800 --> 25:25.000
If I accidentally ruin
my relationship with them

25:25.560 --> 25:28.000
and the advertising department
holds me responsible,

25:28.080 --> 25:29.920
how am I supposed to explain that?

25:31.480 --> 25:33.400
- About this matter…
- I'm sorry.

25:33.480 --> 25:35.080
Regarding what happened at Yihe Daily,

25:35.160 --> 25:38.480
I've already explained it
to Director Gan and Ms. Qian.

25:39.120 --> 25:42.440
I don't understand
how baseless rumors like this

25:42.520 --> 25:45.720
can spread in a news department
that's supposed to be fact-based.

25:45.800 --> 25:48.560
Why do I have to take responsibility
for false accusations?

25:48.640 --> 25:51.480
- False accusations?
- If we, as journalists,

25:51.560 --> 25:54.680
don't pursue the truth,
don't verify facts,

25:55.240 --> 25:56.840
then how are we any different
from gossip tabloids?

25:59.440 --> 26:01.400
Where is our journalistic integrity?

26:06.480 --> 26:08.560
Well said. That was a great point.

26:10.800 --> 26:11.720
Yifan,

26:13.200 --> 26:16.040
you've worked hard this past year.

26:17.400 --> 26:19.160
As journalists,

26:19.680 --> 26:23.520
we must have the spirit to never give up
until we uncover the truth.

26:24.280 --> 26:25.480
But some people

26:26.280 --> 26:29.040
might have forgotten the basics
after working in this field too long.

26:29.720 --> 26:30.720
Isn't that right, Shen?

26:32.160 --> 26:33.960
That's just how I am.

26:34.680 --> 26:36.400
If someone thinks

26:36.480 --> 26:39.200
I got my position through connections,

26:39.280 --> 26:41.280
then I'll do everything in my power

26:41.360 --> 26:43.760
to prove my ability through my work.

26:43.840 --> 26:45.960
I'll use results to shut them up.

26:47.480 --> 26:48.720
Got it?

26:51.240 --> 26:52.400
Thank you, Mr. Gan.

26:53.400 --> 26:54.440
I'll get back to work now.

26:58.240 --> 26:59.640
Let's head out for fieldwork, Mu Chengyun.

26:59.720 --> 27:00.640
Got it!

27:10.760 --> 27:13.040
Yifan, you've finally
broken your bad habit.

27:13.560 --> 27:15.920
Your bad habit
is always putting yourself last.

27:16.000 --> 27:18.840
But what you just said
was so satisfying to hear.

27:18.920 --> 27:19.840
That was awesome.

27:20.600 --> 27:23.480
You shut those bullies up completely.

27:57.400 --> 27:58.360
Want to get drunk?

28:00.720 --> 28:03.160
No. This alcohol isn't that strong.

28:09.120 --> 28:10.160
What's wrong?

28:11.520 --> 28:12.720
Did you forget the rule?

28:14.000 --> 28:15.760
If you're not back by ten,
you need to let me know.

28:19.080 --> 28:20.560
I forgot. Sorry.

28:20.640 --> 28:23.480
I feel like lately, you've been…

28:25.160 --> 28:26.200
a bit distant.

28:27.480 --> 28:30.280
I'm just really tired.
I just want to sleep.

28:30.360 --> 28:31.520
Then sleep…

28:45.640 --> 28:46.840
THE HUMAN PROTAGONIST: YUE XINGHE

29:26.280 --> 29:27.880
So, you sleepwalk

29:28.520 --> 29:31.760
when you're in a bad mood
and when you're drunk?

29:40.440 --> 29:41.600
What's going on today?

29:55.720 --> 29:58.360
Hey, are you about to walk out the door?

30:17.960 --> 30:18.800
What are you looking at?

30:22.440 --> 30:24.240
Why are you acting like a creep?

30:27.520 --> 30:28.520
Where are you going?

30:36.160 --> 30:39.000
You're in the wrong place.
This isn't your room.

30:48.320 --> 30:50.800
Your room is over there. Over there.

30:54.000 --> 30:55.280
Go. Go on.

31:37.240 --> 31:38.280
Where are you going?

31:45.360 --> 31:46.680
Your room is over there.

32:39.960 --> 32:41.560
I moved the sofa again last night.

32:53.480 --> 32:54.520
He didn't come to me.

32:55.360 --> 32:57.760
Does that mean nothing happened?

32:59.760 --> 33:02.280
He can't catch me sleepwalking every time.

33:06.760 --> 33:08.640
YOGURT DRINK

33:29.040 --> 33:32.320
I'm getting used to the breakfast he made.

33:32.400 --> 33:33.960
It's strawberry-flavored, as always.

33:38.880 --> 33:39.920
SUMMER

33:40.000 --> 33:41.240
It was a pleasure
being interviewed by you.

33:41.320 --> 33:42.360
Really?

33:42.440 --> 33:44.800
I used to think
journalists were all aggressive.

33:44.880 --> 33:46.200
I just hope you felt free to speak openly.

33:46.280 --> 33:48.000
- Thank you.
- Thanks. You worked hard today.

33:48.080 --> 33:48.960
You too.

33:51.600 --> 33:52.880
Yifan, you did it!

33:53.480 --> 33:55.840
There are many types of journalists.
Not everyone likes my approach.

33:56.640 --> 33:59.000
No, I think she felt at ease with you.

34:00.040 --> 34:01.360
We're not in the service industry.

34:01.440 --> 34:03.040
Making interviewees comfortable
isn't the only goal.

34:03.120 --> 34:04.960
Seeking the truth is what matters most.

34:05.760 --> 34:08.239
Of course, balancing both would be ideal.

34:08.320 --> 34:10.800
For an intern, you sure talk big.

34:11.360 --> 34:13.080
Aren't you an intern too?

34:13.679 --> 34:16.520
Isn't the point of an internship
to strive to be your best?

34:17.159 --> 34:19.080
Keep it up. Good work today.

34:20.120 --> 34:23.280
Yifan, are you free after work tomorrow?

34:23.360 --> 34:25.360
Tomorrow? Not sure yet.

34:35.239 --> 34:36.280
Everything packed?

34:36.960 --> 34:38.040
It's fine. I'll handle them.

34:40.840 --> 34:41.840
Looks like it's drizzling.

34:44.280 --> 34:45.480
Yifan,

34:45.560 --> 34:48.080
actually, I know a senior.

34:48.159 --> 34:49.080
He just had a baby girl.

34:49.920 --> 34:52.719
So, I want to buy a gift for his daughter.

34:52.800 --> 34:55.040
But I don't know much about these things.

34:55.840 --> 34:59.120
So, I was wondering
if you could come pick one with me.

35:00.120 --> 35:01.360
A daughter?

35:02.560 --> 35:05.840
Then maybe you should ask Zhen Yu.
She has a two-year-old daughter.

35:05.920 --> 35:07.240
She'd know better than I would.

35:07.920 --> 35:10.760
Zhen Yu? I'm not that close with her.

35:10.840 --> 35:12.520
No worries. I can ask her for you.

35:14.840 --> 35:17.040
- Let's go.
- Yifan, wait a second.

35:27.320 --> 35:29.840
I see something on your neck.

35:29.920 --> 35:31.320
I wanted to clean it off for you.

35:33.080 --> 35:35.280
Sorry. It was just instinct.

35:36.280 --> 35:38.400
- Did I hurt you?
- It's fine.

35:39.400 --> 35:41.600
I just didn't expect
such a big reaction from you.

35:45.880 --> 35:48.720
I don't like physical contact. Sorry.

36:08.560 --> 36:09.600
Yifan.

36:11.480 --> 36:13.800
Zhi? What brings you here?

36:14.360 --> 36:16.920
I came to see my brother.
I think he's not back yet.

36:17.440 --> 36:19.400
- Come in and sit for a while.
- Okay.

36:29.760 --> 36:30.760
Have a seat.

36:37.880 --> 36:40.880
Did the college admission results
come out?

36:43.280 --> 36:44.360
Didn't you do well?

36:45.440 --> 36:46.720
I did great.

36:47.800 --> 36:49.240
Which university did you pick?

36:49.920 --> 36:50.960
Yihe University.

36:51.880 --> 36:52.840
Yihe University?

36:54.920 --> 36:57.480
That's pretty far away. Are you sure?

36:57.560 --> 36:58.880
I'm sure.

36:59.760 --> 37:01.400
I thought about it for a long time.

37:01.480 --> 37:02.880
Compared to Nanwu University,

37:02.960 --> 37:05.920
the program I want
is better at Yihe University.

37:06.520 --> 37:08.440
And I don't really want
to stay in Nanwu forever.

37:08.520 --> 37:10.600
I'd like to explore other cities too.

37:12.840 --> 37:13.800
That sounds nice.

37:16.240 --> 37:18.000
But my brother
doesn't seem happy about it.

37:20.800 --> 37:21.840
Why?

37:23.520 --> 37:27.200
Honestly,
I didn't really talk to him about it.

37:27.760 --> 37:29.720
I only discussed it with my parents.

37:31.080 --> 37:34.000
So, he always assumed
I was applying to Nanwu University.

37:34.520 --> 37:35.720
He only found out
about Yihe University recently

37:35.800 --> 37:37.320
and started blaming me.

37:43.520 --> 37:44.880
Your brother…

37:51.600 --> 37:52.440
Sang Yan.

37:53.320 --> 37:56.040
- Unwrap this and plate it.
- Okay.

37:57.760 --> 37:58.600
Let me help.

38:22.760 --> 38:23.960
By the way, Yifan,

38:24.600 --> 38:28.360
do you know who my brother's
rumored high school crush was?

38:32.480 --> 38:35.440
I don't really know.
Why ask about this all of a sudden?

38:36.160 --> 38:37.840
Because I feel like,

38:37.920 --> 38:41.080
in my memory, he looks just as upset now

38:41.160 --> 38:42.720
as he did back when the results came out.

38:43.840 --> 38:46.960
He shut himself in for days,
ignoring everyone.

38:47.040 --> 38:49.160
I think he got dumped.

38:50.280 --> 38:53.480
I feel like my brother
really liked that girl.

38:53.560 --> 38:56.520
Back then, his grades weren't great.

38:56.600 --> 39:00.040
In his second year of high school,
he suddenly changed,

39:01.400 --> 39:03.200
doing nothing but studying.

39:04.480 --> 39:07.640
My parents were so happy.
They thought he finally grew up.

39:08.560 --> 39:10.520
I bet someone had been encouraging him.

39:10.600 --> 39:13.000
I think it was that girl he liked.

39:13.600 --> 39:16.120
- What are you talking about?
- Just girl talk. Is that not allowed?

39:22.600 --> 39:24.920
HEARTBEAT SUMMER EPISODE

39:29.280 --> 39:32.160
Sang Yan, I should've told you earlier
about choosing Yihe University.

39:32.240 --> 39:33.160
That was my mistake.

39:33.720 --> 39:37.680
But I did well
and picked a school and major I love.

39:37.760 --> 39:39.040
Isn't that a good thing?

39:40.880 --> 39:42.280
I just don't like Yihe University.

39:42.880 --> 39:44.560
I've never heard anything bad about it.

39:51.360 --> 39:54.040
Are you done eating? If not, hurry up.

39:54.120 --> 39:55.920
Do I have a time limit on meals here?

39:57.640 --> 40:00.400
Then take a cab home later. I'm tired.

40:00.480 --> 40:01.680
I'm going to sleep.

40:09.800 --> 40:12.440
Yifan, what happened to you?

40:16.000 --> 40:17.760
Maybe I just sleep weird
and bumped into something.

40:18.360 --> 40:20.600
Can bad sleep habits cause that?

40:24.720 --> 40:26.200
Yifan,

40:26.880 --> 40:28.120
do you need any help?

40:28.200 --> 40:29.960
No. Just go home.

40:30.040 --> 40:32.480
Alright. I'll head out then.
I'll come visit you next time.

40:32.560 --> 40:34.000
Stay safe.

40:35.800 --> 40:38.640
You rushed me through the meal so much.
I couldn't even digest properly.

40:38.720 --> 40:41.120
I need to go shopping.
I'll be late if I don't hurry.

40:41.720 --> 40:43.800
So, "tired" was just an excuse?

40:43.880 --> 40:45.360
Don't talk to me. I'm upset.

40:52.120 --> 40:53.600
Your brother…

40:54.480 --> 40:55.840
doesn't want you to go to Yihe University?

40:55.920 --> 40:57.960
The way he reacted was like

40:58.040 --> 40:59.760
when I initially chose Nanwu University

40:59.840 --> 41:02.680
but secretly changed my choice
without telling anyone later.

41:11.200 --> 41:12.720
I want to change my choice.

41:15.560 --> 41:16.320
ONLINE APPLICATION SYSTEM

41:16.400 --> 41:21.560
WEN YIFAN, OPTION A: NANWU UNIVERSITY

41:27.920 --> 41:28.960
Whether you show up or not,

41:30.400 --> 41:31.840
I'll stick to our promise.

41:34.480 --> 41:36.040
WEN YIFAN, OPTION A: NANWU UNIVERSITY

41:36.120 --> 41:37.840
WEN YIFAN, OPTION A: YIHE UNIVERSITY

41:37.920 --> 41:39.520
YOUR APPLICATION HAS BEEN SUBMITTED
TO THE EDUCATION BUREAU DATABASE

41:42.120 --> 41:45.480
In his second year of high school,
he suddenly changed,

41:45.560 --> 41:47.320
doing nothing but studying.

41:48.680 --> 41:50.320
Then he applied to Nanwu University.

41:50.840 --> 41:53.680
When the results came out,
he was so excited.

41:53.760 --> 41:54.960
He bragged to us

41:55.040 --> 41:57.040
that he got into
Nanwu University effortlessly.

41:57.120 --> 41:59.280
Then he left the house, thrilled.

41:59.800 --> 42:01.760
That night, he came back really late.

42:02.280 --> 42:04.280
I bet someone had been encouraging him.

42:04.800 --> 42:06.720
I think it was that girl he liked.

43:58.920 --> 44:03.560
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

44:03.640 --> 44:06.760
Are there night lights?
Something with softer lighting.

44:06.840 --> 44:08.680
Check the second shelf in the cabinet.

44:08.760 --> 44:09.600
- Okay, thanks.
- You're welcome.

47:30.720 --> 47:31.840
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

47:31.920 --> 47:33.040
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
